cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on personalizing image tags based on user preferences, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the use of computer vision techniques (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) to analyze user tagging behavior. Additionally, the paper collects a dataset (cs.MM) to support their observations.
